gov.nih.nci.cbiit.cmts.ui.common
Interface MappableNode

All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultMappableTreeNode, DefaultSourceTreeNode, DefaultTargetTreeNode, FunctionBoxGraphCell, FunctionBoxGraphPort
public interface MappableNode

An interface to indicate whether the subject has participated in mapping or not. The implementation of this interface will help UI render to present different cues to indicate its (mapping) status. Also the implementation class shall define an instance member variable to remember the status.

Since:
CMTS v1.0
